headline.print_headline: Knicks Open Jackson Era With Seventh Straight Win
headline.main: Knicks Open Jackson Era With Seventh Straight Win

lead_paragraph: Phil Jackson was given a rousing welcome home by the Madison Square Garden crowd and the gift of a victory by the New York Knicks, whose future he now oversees as the team's new chief of basketball operations.
